net.sf.appia.protocols.group.events
Class GroupEvent

java.lang.Object
  net.sf.appia.core.Event

All Implemented Interfaces:

Direct Known Subclasses:
BlockOk, Fail, NewView, OtherViews, PreView, View, ViewChange
public class GroupEvent
extends Event
implements java.lang.Cloneable

Superclass of all Events generated by the Group Communication protocols that are not sendable.
It exetends the regular Event by adding the group id and the view id. These attributes are mandatory.

Version:
0.1
Author:
Alexandre Pinto
See Also:
GroupSendableEvent
